      "span_text": "Thymocytes were harvested prior to CD25 down-regulation and cycling (6 hours) and when a significant fraction of RAG-1-deficient thymocytes are cycling (24 hours). Upon the induction of pre-TCR signaling total as well as active ␤-catenin levels did not increase, strongly suggesting that ␤-catenin was not stabilized by pre-TCR signaling ( Figure 5C )."
